Fix for Bug #48578 (available from GangaGUI-20-4) should have been in for 5.3.0 but for some reason
did not make it in. GangaGUI-20-5 includes this fix.

Removed sorting for Job builder list view to allow developers to dictate the sequence of attribute
display by using the _GUIPrefs and _GUIAdvancedPrefs lists. Note that if there are any attributes
are not specified explicitly (in _GUIPrefs and _GUIAdvancedPrefs), the order will be that which the
schema dictionary returns its keys. Of course, those already specified will be displayed as expected.


